Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}土壇場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}構うか !!
